The "Team" tab on the dashboard is very useful for organizing groups of spaces and, in particular, focusing what is shown in the "Recently Updated" section.  The problem is that only space admins can add team labels so users can't create their own groups of spaces to be displayed on the dashboards.  Adding the ability for users to specify their own team labels (e.g. my:neatspace) would solve this problem provide you also populate the dropdown box on the "Team" tab with each users own labels.

